<p>Send TRTL to this address</p>

<p><code>TRTLv12WtKJAzTNtxSkbcXf7mjeVApSqRYACtoJE2X52UBSce7qGAQ1JQgG3MmArnZSbkJXKqBXiPX2Mno7xD4tqD3p8SySoBc5</code></p>

<p>With this Payment ID <strong>!! IMPORTANT !!</strong></p>

