<h4 id='wow-megatip-wat'>Wow? Megatip wat?</h4>
<p>An idea has been floated regarding a Megatip function. Basically, someone could purposely send a large chunk of TRTL and most of it would be sent out in the next wave of rain tips. </p>

<p>If you want to see something like this, talk about it! ;)</p>
